race.comment: BATTLE ON BATTLER (2) is racing in good order, finishing 1.1L off the winner last time out at this track and trip. He jumped the race favourite there for the apprentice hoop and now gets Yuill in the saddle. Needs some luck from the barrier but his recent figures suggest he's going well enough to win this. STRAPPING PROPHET (1) is third-up here following a good run in a CL3 at Northam 10 days ago. He's likely to find this a little easier and the rise to 1400m is a big tick. He's right back in grade today and with his upside, this looks a race well within his grasp. SCURGEOFTHEWEST (3) resumed in good order with a 0.5L defeat here last start when running on from the back. The rise in trip suits him and he maps for a lovely run in transit. Can make his presence felt. SPECIAL PLAN (7) led them up last start over this track and trip and knocked up late. Fitter now and can improve. GAV HAS SPOKEN (8) is next best.
